Interface CachableHttpServletRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, javax.servlet.ServletRequest
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SpringCachableHttpServletRequest

    public interface CachableHttpServletRequest
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest
    Interface specifying a cachable HTTP Servlet Request where input data is cached and can be run multiple times. Created by Philip Vendil on 2018-10-25.
